name: Pizza Zucchini
description: Pizza and zucchini haven’t been close culinary friends, until now! Crispy fries meet iconic pizza flavours. And hey, we’re not in the habit of telling you what to do, but you should really try dunking these in warm Marinara Sauce.
preparation: Whisk egg white with milk in a small bowl.
Combine Parmesan, breadcrumbs, and seasoning in a separate bowl.
Dip zucchini sticks into egg mixture, and then roll in breadcrumb mixture.
Place on a crisper and bake for 25–30 minutes or until golden brown.
tips: Serve with warm Marinara Sauce or kick up the heat with Chipotle Aioli.
perfectlyBalanceYourPlate: Serve with 1 protein serving and 1 cup veggies.
